==發行==
《科洛弗悖論》由[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]排定於2017年10月27日在美國廣泛上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=J.J. Abrams' 'God's Particle' Gets 2017 Date|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jj-abrams-gods-particle-gets-866557|accessdate=2016-05-06|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-02-16|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103901/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jj-abrams-gods-particle-gets-866557|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年7月，該片延期至2018年2月2日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/paramount-2017-cloverfield-movie-2018-1202502280/|title=Paramount Pushes ‘Cloverfield Movie’ Back to 2018|work=Variety|author=Dave McNary|date=2017-07-21|access-date=2017-08-13|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308233234/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/paramount-2017-cloverfield-movie-2018-1202502280/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年1月2日，宣布，該片的上映日再度改至2018年4月20日<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2018/film/news/god-particle-cloverfield-release-date-postponed-1202651936/|title=J.J. Abrams’ Next ‘Cloverfield’ Installment ‘God Particle’ Shifts Release Date Again|work=Variety|author=Erin Nyren|date=2018-01-03|access-date=2018-01-04|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109030833/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/god-particle-cloverfield-release-date-postponed-1202651936/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年1月，該片的上映日和片名《上帝粒子》都被刪去<ref name="TitleDropped">{{cite news |url=http://ca.ign.com/articles/2018/01/03/cloverfield-3-delayed-again-may-have-new-title |title=Cloverfield 3 Delayed Again, May Have New Title |first=Matt |last=Davidson |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2018-01-03 |accessdate=2018-01-11}}</ref>。同月，據透露，[[Netflix|Netflix]]有意向派拉蒙收購該片。派拉蒙影業的董事吉姆·吉諾普洛斯認為，該片的預算過高，以致對該片用傳統的戲院發行幾乎沒有利潤。此外，亞柏拉罕原有意全力投入後製的工作，但為期已晚<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/netflix-talks-acquire-cloverfield-sequel-paramount-1077752 |title=Netflix in Talks to Acquire 'Cloverfield' Sequel From Paramount |last=Kit |first=Borys |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2018-01-23 |accessdate=2018-01-24 |archive-date=2018-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124064614/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/netflix-talks-acquire-cloverfield-sequel-paramount-1077752 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年2月4日，該片定名《科洛弗悖論》並釋出首支預告片，同時也於同天在Netflix發行（{{link-en|第52屆超級盃|Super Bowl LII}}結束後隨即上架）<ref name="sb">{{cite web | url = https://deadline.com/2018/02/cloverfield-sequel-god-particle-super-bowl-trailer-netflix-streaming-release-1202276386/ | title = Netflix’s Ultimate Super Bowl Surprise: ‘The Cloverfield Paradox’ – Watch Trailer | first = Anthony | last = D'Alessandro | date = 2018-02-04 | accessdate = 2018-02-04 | work = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | archive-date = 2018-02-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180205003638/http://deadline.com/2018/02/cloverfield-sequel-god-particle-super-bowl-trailer-netflix-streaming-release-1202276386/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。據報導，Netflix支付了超過5000萬美元來獲得該片的版權<ref name="thr 50m">{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/netflix-paid-paramount-more-50-million-cloverfield-paradox-1082305 | title = Sources: Netflix Paid Paramount More Than $50 Million for 'Cloverfield Paradox' | first1 = Borys | last1 = Kit | first2 = Pamela | last2 = McClintonk | date = 2018-02-06 | accessdate = 2018-02-06 | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-date = 2018-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180207021339/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/netflix-paid-paramount-more-50-million-cloverfield-paradox-1082305 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===評價===
《科洛弗悖論》獲得了負面居多的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據107條評論，新鮮度持有17%，平均得分4.5 / 10<ref>{{cite web |title=''The Cloverfield Paradox'' (2018) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_cloverfield_paradox |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |4= |publisher=Fandango |accessdate=2018-02-07 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416054917/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_cloverfield_paradox |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，則獲得了37分<ref>{{cite web |title=''The Cloverfield Paradox'' Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |3= |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-cloverfield-paradox |accessdate=2018-02-06 |archive-date=2020-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229043136/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-cloverfield-paradox |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

儘管該片收穫普遍負評，但在超級盃當天宣布該片並在數小時後推出的營銷方式被Netflix視為一種新穎的方式。[[IGN|IGN]]指出，這種策略只適用於一個特定的系列電影，而大部分的新電影則需要一個重要的營銷期間來吸引觀眾<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2018/02/05/the-cloverfield-gimmick-how-netflix-tricked-the-world | title = The Cloverfield Gimmick: How Netflix Tricked The World | first = William | last = Bibbiani | date = 2018-02-05 | accessdate = 2018-02-05 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | archive-date = 2020-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201106151619/https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/02/05/the-cloverfield-gimmick-how-netflix-tricked-the-world | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

